       The Advantage of Internationalization: Why go "against a sea of troubles"?
       **** Learning Objectives ****
          1. Analyze how internationalization enables companies to increase their value
2            propositions and understand the nature of such benefits.                   CEMEX
          2. Learn how to evaluate potential internationalization strategies.
          3. Anticipate the organizational and individual challenges of
